# Data layer

- Lessons: inline in `lessons.ts`, keyed by `topicId` from `topics.ts`
- Books: `book-catalog.ts` (metadata) + `summaries.json` (generated slides)
- Public API in `index.ts`: `getBook`, `getLesson`, `getTopic`, `books`, `lessons` — extend these, don't bypass
- Never read entire `summaries.json`; grep by book id
- Regenerate books with `generate_content.py` (see `docs/CONTENT_PIPELINE.md`)
